<title>USA: Omega names chief financial officer.</title>
<headline>Omega names chief financial officer.</headline>
<dateline>BOTHELL, Wash. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Omega Environmental Inc said Tuesday it has appointed Jeffery Weinress as chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Weinress replaces Dan Steigerwald, who has resigned to pursue other business opportunities.</p>
<p>Weinress joined Omega as executive vice president in 1995 and has, among other things, managed a restructuring that cut Omega's workforce by about 30 percent.</p>
